window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> &amp; </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> best-selling author Rina Kent comes a sizzling dark enemies-to-lovers romance filled with a thrilling chase between a mafia prince and a psychology nerd.</b></p> <p>I’m trapped by the devil.</p> <p>What started as an innocent mistake turned into actual hell.</p> <p>In my defense, I didn’t mean to get involved with a mafia prince.</p> <p>But he barged through my defenses anyway.</p> <p>He stalked me from the shadows and stole me from the life I know.</p> <p>Jeremy Volkov might appear charming, but a true predator lurks inside.</p> <p>He’s out to possess, own, and keep me.</p> <p>But I have no plans to stick around in his blood-soaked world.</p> <p>Or so I think.</p> <p><b>Tropes:</b></p> <ul> <li>Antihero x good girl</li> <li>Enemies to lovers</li> <li>He stalks her</li> <li>Mafia backdrop</li> </ul> <p><i>This audiobook is a dark unconventional romance and contains themes that aren't to everyone's liking. Please check the author's note in the ebook for content warnings before listening.</i></p> <p><i>This audiobook has been re-recorded in duet format as of November 2025</i></p>"; 
